here are excerpts from a translation of 
iraqi president saddam husseins address to moslems on sunday 
carried on iraqi state television and radio on the occasion of the 
birthday of the prophet mohammed 
 
we have said on more than one occasion that the infidels have 
not carried out aggression against the people of faith in iraq 
because of the events that took place after aug 2 their 
aggressive actions took place long before aug 2 even the american 
decision to impose a bread embargo on iraq began before aug 2 
besides even before aug 2 there was talk in america and europe 
of exploring ways of boycotting iraq 
this provides enough documented evidence that they harbored 
aggressive intentions using the pretext of what they called iraqs 
dangerous and growing military might its developing industry and 
the military industrialization of our country and our remark on 
april 4 in response to aggressive postures and statements that 
whoever strikes at iraq or any other arabs we will hit back 
strongly these statements were cover by the west for aggression in 
the form of political informational and economic actions 
after the criminals realized that all these aggressive actions 
had not prevented iraq from its program to call for and demand the 
liberation of palestine narrow the gap between the poor and the 
rich and use oil within a humanitarian and rational policy they 
pushed the croesus of kuwait and his supporters the backward sheiks 
in kuwait and other places to play their shameless treacherous role 
in plotting against iraq and to weaken it with the aim of 
achieving their disappointed aspirations 
instead of relinquishing our principles the honor involved in 
the right and responsible position and the great iraqi peoples 
role the blow was directed at the croesus of kuwait and his 
supporters and by this defensive and revolutionary measure which 
achieved an unprecedented success with the help of god the usurped 
right of faithful iraq was restored a right on which the throne of 
corruption had been established until kuwait had been deprived of 
any light during the past period 
the infidel people and the enemies of the arab nation who 
betrayed the arab nation went out of their mind and realized that 
the punishment inflicted on those who appeared on the stage of 
hostility to the line of faith and struggle to liberate palestine 
would increase the ability of faith and the faithful and help 
spread right and diminish the influence of falsehood therefore 
armies and fleets came from every evil corner led by the haven of 
evil in the united states instead of learning the lesson of aug 2 
to stay away from plans and measures preceding the event they 
began as usual with those who fall into the abyss and whose 
behavior is dominated by satan and grudge to increase their forces 
and commit another crime against god his messenger and the 
faithful by occupying the land of the arab and moslem sanctities in 
the arabian peninsula and the arabian gulf 
the iraqi armed forces will be prepared to stay alert ready to 
face any eventuality and prepared to defend the province of kuwait 
the same way it would defend any other province in the country 
the arab solution can only be achieved in an atmosphere of good 
arab relations since good arab relations cannot be conceived in 
the presence of foreign forces on arab lands and moslem holy places 
and under threats these forces must go 
should the international community be involved in a solution to 
the crisis then the emphasis should be on the initiative of aug 
12 1990 which underlined that peace could not be achieved 
without the settlement of all problems of the region 
withdrawal of foreign forces from the lands of najd and hejaz 
saudi arabia and the arabian gulf and ending the blockade of 
iraq is a slogan for all arabs and believers to raise 
in all cases we must encourage every foreign move including 
those made by those who were involved in amassing the fleets to 
retreat without bargaining over our objectives and principles we 
should also regard any retreat that is based on the fact that the 
picture was not clear at the beginning as a virtue for those who 
make this retreat therefore we view the speech of the french 
president despite certain reservations as being of a different 
language and we hope our positive interpretation is correct 
difference in opinion does not annoy us what annoys us is the 
grudgefilled baseless accusations by certain leaders unwilling to 
discuss our perceptions and interpretations 
it is not important to agree or disagree with this initiative or 
that including that of french president mitterrand what is 
important is that a serious dialogue be launched in search of a 
possible just and comprehensive solution that would allow peace to 
prevail and lay solid foundations for the future of the concerned 
people of the region that are not shaken by circumstantial changes 
we intend to launch contact with the french government with the 
aim of formulating a precise viewpoint so that action could 
be launched on clear and solid foundations 
our main concern is that the situation that prevailed before 
aug 2 on all levels may not be repeated that palestine returns to 
its people the palestinians so they can set up their independent 
state and the foreign occupation forces depart from the land of 
najd hejaz saudi arabia and the gulf without any conditions 
