assure safeguards in the latin countries nuclear programs 
bush and the latin leaders also discussed efforts to forge a 
common market of brazil argentina uruguay and paraguay and their 
desire to see the general agreement on tariffs and trade produce a 
breakthrough on lowering trade barriers around the world 
bush told menem the united states shares argentinas concerns 
about the agricultural subsidies that the european community 
provides its farmers aronson said 
