that award after ruling that mcdonald was entitled to absolute 
immunity under north carolina common law 
in the appeal acted on today smith argued that the states 
common law provides only qualified not absolute immunity from 
lawsuits in such circumstances 
the case is smith vs mcdonald 891818 
