war has grown significantly as sanctions and a hostile world push 
saddam into a corner with no diplomatic escape 
i think another six to eight weeks is available to prevent a 
conflict but after that it becomes almost inevitable said paul 
beaver publisher of the respected janes defense weekly in an 
interview in london 
such reports prompted the israeli army to announce today that it 
will begin distributing gas masks to israels 47 million citizens 
next week 
the announcement follows threats by saddam to attack israel 
including one in which he said he would burn half the jewish state 
with chemical weapons 
the official iraqi news agency said today that saddam has 
ordered the release of nine french nationals they are believed to 
be among the westerners saddam has ordered placed at strategic 
sites to serve as shields to prevent potential western attacks 
on sunday in a speech on iraqi state tv and radio saddam said 
he no longer opposes involvement by foreign powers in seeking a 
settlement to the crisis which was precipitated by iraqs aug 2 
invasion of kuwait 
