threatened to hit israel with binary chemical weapons and make 
fire eat half of israel in retaliation for an israeli nuclear 
attack 
israel in 1981 bombed a nuclear reactor near baghdad saying 
iraq was using it to develop weapons 
saddams threats intensified after iraqs aug 2 invasion of 
kuwait 
