now we dont have any actual information stating god forbid that 
hostilities will start tonight or tomorrow or in a week or two 
still signs of public anxiety emerged minutes after the army 
announcement 
i never thought that would happen when i heard it today my 
first thought was oh my god this is not a joke said margo 
iyoun a 29yearold immigrant from orinda calif 
coming and living in israel that for me was an idealistic 
thing but its hard to leave anything on the level of idealism 
when you have a child 
the only previous distribution of gas masks was experimental it 
was conducted 1 years ago in two towns and was declared successful 
after the army found the population kept the kits in good shape 
