each morning with a cheery good morning geniuses has to cope 
with the impact of a flu epidemic on a citywide high school 
shakespeare competition 
there might not be an epidemic at his school were it not for 
arvid obsessed with maintaining a perfect attendance record he 
insists on coming to class even tough hes so stricken by flu he 
faints at the start of the show 
this prompts macgregor to tell him you look like something 
the cat dragged in changed its mind dragged back out again came 
back in threw up went back out dragged it farther away and 
diiiiiiiied 
its not said meanly though but in the caring tradition and 
