they seemed to have a similar feeling for me gill said i 
think its a good calling card to have them in your camp 
the album includes dance hall swing tunes rodeo songs and 
contemporary pop music 
weve got a real good chance to go gold gill said we 
even got on the pop charts for awhile its been fun 
looking back im kind of thankful in a way that the success 
didnt happen right away thats real dangerous to go to the top 
and be the rage it doesnt allow time to build the way down might 
be just as quick 
he has no regrets about choosing music as a career instead of 
golf 
music is more fun much more creative i love golf but music 
is much more rewarding by writing songs and communicating with 
folks he said 
thats the true godgiven talent i was given i dont think a 
golf swing is my best blessing i can sing a little better than i 
can make a fourfooter 
