all kinds of strategies to pass his two years of bed rest in 
saranac lake starting in 1934 
once he recalled being chided by a doctor just for playing 
chess with another patient 
time still had a way of going by he said 
people who were ambulatory would come in the nurses would 
come in he said each thing was an event a highlight i would 
