patterson now a student at the state university of new york at 
plattsburgh requested copies of his personal fbi file in 1987 
the request made under the freedom of information act was 
denied patterson was told the files could not be released because 
of national security reasons 
some information from the files subsequently was released but 
the rest remained classified 
patterson sued the fbi and an unknown government agency in 1988 
seeking full disclosure of the files and monetary damages 
in response to his lawsuit the government offered to expunge 
his name from all fbi records the offer was not accepted 
