remainder shelf in a discount book shop it eventually became 
once on this island 
the story set in the french antilles is simple and sweet it 
tells the tale of i moune a darkskinned peasant girl who falls 
in love with a wealthy young mulatto she saves his life but he 
marries among his own class ti moune dies of a broken heart but 
the gods take pity on her they transform her into a tree to guard 
the young mans home 
the pair wrote once on this island in about six months 
we made an outline of the scenes ahrens recalls we said 
this or that will happen here and then we just started coming up 
with the songs and the songs became the story 
