the steering committee of londons stock exchange said monday it 
would remove polly peck shares from the financial timesstock 
exchange 100share index effective immediately 
the index represents britains top 100 stocks in terms of market 
capitalization and the exchanges committee adjusts the index at 
least four times a year 
food and commodities concern dalgety plc will replace polly peck 
in the key index beginning tuesday the stock exchange said 
